Package org.svvrl.goal.core.tran.modella

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Cover
    A Cover is a set of CoverElement, which means one of the element should be satisfied.
    CoverElement
    A CoverElement is a set of LTL formulae (literals or formulae of the form "() f") that should be satisfied at the same time.
    ExtendedModella
    This class provides an implementation of an extended MoDeLLa translation algorithm.
    ExtendedModellaTranslators
    This class provides several translators based on the extended MoDeLLa approach.
    ExtendedModellaTranslators.LTL2LOSNBW
    This is a translator from a LTL formula to a label-on-state NBW based on the extended MoDeLLa approach.
    ExtendedModellaTranslators.LTL2LOSNGBW
    This is a translator from a LTL formula to a label-on-state NGBW based on the extended MoDeLLa approach.
